Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.67,0:00:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda! This isn't child's play! Don't be flippant!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.11,0:00:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.73,0:00:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is about the Kira investigation! {\alpha&HFF&}Will you take it seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.06,0:00:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is about the Kira investigation! Will you take it seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.90,0:00:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.04,0:00:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.79,0:00:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, Matsuda-san, please stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.44,0:00:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Matsuda"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.45,0:00:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be a dead weight around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.06,0:00:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-{\alpha&HFF&}Ryuuzaki, is there anything else I can do? Other than being a manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ryuuzaki, {\alpha&HFF&}is there anything else I can do? Other than being a manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.70,0:00:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ryuuzaki, is there anything else I can do? {\alpha&HFF&}Other than being a manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.02,0:00:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ryuuzaki, is there anything else I can do? Other than being a manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, can you bring me another cup of coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.54,0:00:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I too... {\alpha&HFF&}want to play a bigger role in this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I too... want to play a bigger role in this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.09,0:00:37.14,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs72\pos(362,355)}Matsuda
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.77,0:00:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.66,0:00:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please, {\alpha&HFF&}don't tell me that you're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.51,0:00:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please, don't tell me that you're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.15,0:00:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be by your side forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.80,0:00:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Director!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.73,0:00:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Misa has a boyfriend, so love scenes are no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.68,0:00:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! W-Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:00:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:00:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can just pretend to kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.66,0:01:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you say things like that, we'll never get this movie finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.20,0:01:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said no, and I mean no!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.85,0:01:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Yotsuba Group's Tokyo Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.47,0:01:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is Friday!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.59,0:01:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the deaths which benefit Yotsuba happen towards the end of the week.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be a dead weight around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.02,0:01:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was always something amazing about Mogi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.84,0:01:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda! {\alpha&HFF&}This isn't child's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.85,0:01:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda! This isn't child's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.94,0:01:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you take it seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.25,0:01:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Matsuda-san is a bit of an airhead by nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.99,0:01:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me another cup of coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.58,0:01:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.40,0:01:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsu! {\alpha&HFF&}Hey, Matsu!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.96,0:01:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsu! Hey, Matsu!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.92,0:01:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems to have gone off somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.51,0:01:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.51,0:02:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, {\alpha&HFF&}let's try starting with the names on this list.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, let's try starting with the names on this list.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.12,0:02:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.67,0:02:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it was possible to kill someone by merely knowing their name and face, {\alpha&HFF&}would I try to kill criminals?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.81,0:02:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it was possible to kill someone by merely knowing their name and face, would I try to kill criminals?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do believe there are people in this world that are better off dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.55,0:02:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I wouldn't take it upon myself and become a murderer to make the world a better place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.58,0:02:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm thinking about this too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.78,0:02:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'd forget about killing so many people--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.23,0:02:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.11,0:02:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you staring at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you annoyed that I'm the only one with cake to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.76,0:02:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.41,0:02:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.99,0:02:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not envious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Watari?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:03:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The detective Erald Coil has been commissioned to "reveal L's identity".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erald Coil, the famous detective said to be second only to L.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would commission this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.60,0:03:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've determined that the commission came from Kida Masahiko, the Planning Director of the Yotsuba Group's Tokyo Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it is Yotsuba's work!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yotsuba has got to be working with Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They want L's identity, {\alpha&HFF&}so that they can kill L.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.49,0:03:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They want L's identity, so that they can kill L.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad. {\alpha&HFF&}We're already understaffed, and now we have this Coil to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.36,0:03:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad. We're already understaffed, and now we have this Coil to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.51,0:03:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The detective known as Erald Coil is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three most famous detectives in this world at the moment... {\alpha&HFF&}L, Coil and Deneuve... are all me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three most famous detectives in this world at the moment... L, {\alpha&HFF&}Coil and Deneuve... are all me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three most famous detectives in this world at the moment... L, Coil {\alpha&HFF&}and Deneuve... are all me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three most famous detectives in this world at the moment... L, Coil and Deneuve... {\alpha&HFF&}are all me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three most famous detectives in this world at the moment... L, Coil and Deneuve... are all me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of people who try to find me fall for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep this secret, {\alpha&HFF&}this strawberry is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.81,0:03:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep this secret, this strawberry is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.44,0:04:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive as always, Ryuuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.59,0:04:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be better to try and blend in and get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.16,0:04:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! {\alpha&HFF&}Then me coming here would mean nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Then me coming here would mean nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I wait for everyone to go before searching the building?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what if I get caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.47,0:04:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's better if I leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, tonight again? {\alpha&HFF&}I'm really not in the mood for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, tonight again? I'm really not in the mood for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.92,0:04:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least it's the weekend; {\alpha&HFF&}if we had these drawn out secret meetings on a Monday, it'd be hard for me to bring myself to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least it's the weekend; if we had these drawn out secret meetings on a Monday, it'd be hard for me to bring myself to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.89,0:04:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Secret meetings?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.71,0:04:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.63,0:04:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The nineteenth floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:05:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come this far...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.13,0:05:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, {\alpha&HFF&}I've got to get close to this guy? Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.63,0:05:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I've got to get close to this guy? {\alpha&HFF&}Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I've got to get close to this guy? Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, {\alpha&HFF&}you want me to hack the surveillance cameras and security system at Yotsuba Group's Tokyo Headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you want me to hack the surveillance cameras and security system at Yotsuba Group's Tokyo Headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.89,0:05:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's safe to assume that there's definitely a connection between Kira and the Yotsuba Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, we need to investigate Yotsuba, {\alpha&HFF&}and determine exactly who, and how many, have this power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, we need to investigate Yotsuba, and determine exactly who, {\alpha&HFF&}and how many, have this power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, we need to investigate Yotsuba, and determine exactly who, and how many, have this power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most importantly, we must ensure that the Yotsuba Group doesn't discover that we're investigating them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.72,0:06:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just consider that if you're caught, our chance of catching Kira will disappear then and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, I can't hear this clearly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could just overhear one important thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.78,0:06:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just in our way... we should kill him and let our share prices rise...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They just said "kill"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.68,0:06:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira-sama is really...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.67,0:06:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kira"?! {\alpha&HFF&}They said "Kira"! They said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kira"?! They said "Kira"! {\alpha&HFF&}They said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.47,0:06:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kira"?! They said "Kira"! They said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're getting Kira to kill someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I heard it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.15,0:06:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're definitely connected to Kira. {\alpha&HFF&}I did it! What an achievement!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're definitely connected to Kira. I did it! What an achievement!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.45,0:06:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, think ahead carefully before you act, {\alpha&HFF&}and don't do anything rash.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, think ahead carefully before you act, and don't do anything rash.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.40,0:06:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Watari?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.46,0:07:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've received a distress signal from Matsuda-san's belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where from?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.51,0:07:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, {\alpha&HFF&}it seems to be originating from Yotsuba Group's Tokyo Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.94,0:07:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it seems to be originating from Yotsuba Group's Tokyo Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm Matsui Tarou, a manager at Yoshida Productions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.27,0:07:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How would you like to hire our number one recommended, multi-talented star, Amane Misa, for your commercials?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, just forget everything I've just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.70,0:07:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to rethink our plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda, you idiot...
Comment: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EYECATCHERS
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshida Productions... {\alpha&HFF&}Matsui Tarou...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshida Productions... Matsui Tarou...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't seem to have anything suspicious on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt he's an industrial spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:08:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... erm, I hope you will consider Misa-Misa...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.68,0:08:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These two are most likely keeping an eye on me, while the rest of them are in the meeting room, deciding how to dispose of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.58,0:08:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm as good as dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they've received my distress signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.56,0:08:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Ryuuzaki will bother to try and save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's going to happen to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.71,0:08:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright, you can answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.76,0:08:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't mention that you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, hold the phone away from your ear so that we can listen in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-{\alpha&HFF&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.71,0:08:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.44,0:08:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Matsui!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Asahi, long time no talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Asahi, how's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't sound like you're outside... {\alpha&HFF&}you at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.73,0:08:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't sound like you're outside... you at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Err, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:08:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm alone. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not with Amane Misa, {\alpha&HFF&}Matsuda is alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.15,0:09:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not with Amane Misa, Matsuda is alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fancy going out for a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Now? {\alpha&HFF&}Sorry, not tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Now? Sorry, not tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, don't tell me your finances are in a pinch again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.66,0:09:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pinch"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.19,0:09:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they're in quite a "pinch" at the moment. You got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.86,0:09:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda is in quite a pinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind, {\alpha&HFF&}another time then. See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind, another time then. See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So, what do you think of Misa-Misa? {\alpha&HFF&}I'm sure she'll be an asset to your company.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.99,0:09:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So, what do you think of Misa-Misa? I'm sure she'll be an asset to your company.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.74,0:09:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're serious about promoting her, shouldn't you have brought her here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really her manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.06,0:09:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she's currently shooting a movie nearby, I'll call her over as soon as she's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.79,0:10:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please consider using Misa-Misa as your image in your commercials.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.36,0:10:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, I've got to keep stalling!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.44,0:10:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa's phone is going straight to the answering machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send a message telling her to call us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.86,0:10:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Ryuuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, {\alpha&HFF&}if Matsuda-san dies now, it'll confirm the Yotsuba Group's guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.52,0:10:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, if Matsuda-san dies now, it'll confirm the Yotsuba Group's guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the moment, let's just see what unfolds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.80,0:10:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It all depends on whether or not he overheard our discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The possibility's there. {\alpha&HFF&}There's no other choice than to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The possibility's there. There's no other choice than to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.99,0:10:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But is he really here merely to promote a "talent"? {\alpha&HFF&}Surely he's not from the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But is he really here merely to promote a "talent"? Surely he's not from the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible. {\alpha&HFF&}The Japanese police should have abandoned the Kira investigation by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible. The Japanese police should have abandoned the Kira investigation by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.47,0:10:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter who he is, {\alpha&HFF&}we've got to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.45,0:10:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter who he is, we've got to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.04,0:10:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that she might actually be a good image for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.57,0:11:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you agree?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her shoot should finish soon, {\alpha&HFF&}so please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.81,0:11:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her shoot should finish soon, so please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, I'm so tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.93,0:11:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, a message from Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.38,0:11:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be worried about me, since it's so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.54,0:11:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light! I'm sorry, but I've been working all this time. I'm done now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.88,0:11:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, {\alpha&HFF&}you're not with Matsuda-san then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.77,0:11:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, you're not with Matsuda-san then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.09,0:11:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's such a disgrace. He just abandoned Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.77,0:11:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My work cell phone is ringing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's Matsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda-san is calling Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask Misa-san to enable us to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa-Misa, {\alpha&HFF&}as soon as filming finishes, I need you to head over to the Yotsuba Group's Tokyo Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.67,0:11:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa-Misa, as soon as filming finishes, I need you to head over to the Yotsuba Group's Tokyo Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.11,0:11:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could get the chance to appear in their commercials.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:11:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, I'm in the middle of negotiating a deal for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.60,0:12:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?! That's amazing, Matsu! So that's what you were doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa will give it everything she got!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, {\alpha&HFF&}take a taxi, and you'll be here in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, take a taxi, and you'll be here in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun, {\alpha&HFF&}we may be able to save Matsuda-san, but we will need Misa-san's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun, we may be able to save Matsuda-san, {\alpha&HFF&}but we will need Misa-san's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.61,0:12:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun, we may be able to save Matsuda-san, but we will need Misa-san's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.04,0:12:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll listen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.14,0:12:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, I'm Misa-Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa doesn't do nudes, but underwear or swimsuits are fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, {\alpha&HFF&}she's ridiculously cute in the flesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, she's ridiculously cute in the flesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely that's not the issue right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.72,0:12:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsu, {\alpha&HFF&}the production company gave the go-ahead for a special reception especially for Yotsuba-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.93,0:12:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsu, the production company gave the go-ahead for a special reception especially for Yotsuba-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? {\alpha&HFF&}Special?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Special?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.93,0:12:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening! {\alpha&HFF&}Pleased to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening! Pleased to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, the girls from our production team would like to provide you all with a special reception!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.95,0:12:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, {\alpha&HFF&}I think we're starting to go off on a tangent here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.85,0:13:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, I think we're starting to go off on a tangent here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.54,0:13:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped; {\alpha&HFF&}for now, we've got to stay close to that manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped; for now, we've got to stay close to that manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.44,0:13:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we may as well enjoy ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.29,0:13:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki and the others should be able to see us in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We might be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, drink up! Drink up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.97,0:13:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This has got to be heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.86,0:13:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa-san... {\alpha&HFF&}she's not bad at this, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa-san... she's not bad at this, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.47,0:13:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, {\alpha&HFF&}can you see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, can you see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:13:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:14:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind about that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.57,0:14:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. {\alpha&HFF&}The eight that are here were in a meeting together, planning who to have Kira murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.85,0:14:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. The eight that are here {\alpha&HFF&}were in a meeting together, planning who to have Kira murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. The eight that are here were in a meeting together, planning who to have Kira murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.91,0:14:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard them clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.38,0:14:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without a doubt, it's them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.52,0:14:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you absolutely sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's true, they'll be aiming to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.20,0:14:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought as much. {\alpha&HFF&}Is there really no way to save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought as much. Is there really no way to save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.32,0:14:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luckily, you're still alive, so there's a chance that we can save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.90,0:14:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to do that... {\alpha&HFF&}you've got to die before you're killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.35,0:14:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to do that... you've got to die before you're killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.94,0:14:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand? {\alpha&HFF&}Listen carefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.01,0:14:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand? Listen carefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.03,0:14:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.29,0:15:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm so drunk...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.94,0:15:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.55,0:15:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everyone! {\alpha&HFF&}Are you all having fun? You should be!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everyone! Are you all having fun? {\alpha&HFF&}You should be!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.05,0:15:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everyone! Are you all having fun? You should be!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.92,0:15:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now everyone, {\alpha&HFF&}this is what you've all been waiting for! It's Matsui Tarou Showtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now everyone, this is what you've all been waiting for! {\alpha&HFF&}It's Matsui Tarou Showtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.29,0:15:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now everyone, this is what you've all been waiting for! It's Matsui Tarou Showtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.10,0:15:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what the hell do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.55,0:15:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Go for it, Matsui-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.52,0:15:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Woo-aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! That's dangerous! You're drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, I do this all the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:15:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's dangerous, you idiot!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.07,0:15:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He fell!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.22,0:16:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! I heard a huge bang and came out to see what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,119! 119!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:31.09,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,119 is the emergency telephone number in Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God... what an awful role to play...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this to us, gentlemen. Hurry up and get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.31,0:16:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.81,0:16:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be fine. {\alpha&HFF&}Please, keep me in mind for the commercial.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.11,0:16:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be fine. Please, keep me in mind for the commercial.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! {\alpha&HFF&}If the paparazzi catch us, it'll be troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.49,0:16:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! If the paparazzi catch us, it'll be troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.78,0:16:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, what's going on?! A jumper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.83,0:16:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at least he died in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.61,0:17:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know we're understaffed, but I can't believe I got dragged into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.75,0:17:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda, you idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.93,0:17:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amane Misa's manager, dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.50,0:17:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the Planning Director at Yotsuba Group's Tokyo Headquarters, Kida Masahiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.57,0:17:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that is correct. {\alpha&HFF&}Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that is correct. Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.66,0:17:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name's Erald Coil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like your advice on a certain issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An advance of $2 million, {\alpha&HFF&}and $8 million for a successful completion? Is he serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:18:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An advance of $2 million, and $8 million for a successful completion? {\alpha&HFF&}Is he serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An advance of $2 million, and $8 million for a successful completion? Is he serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, he's demanded $2 million for his silence if we don't go ahead with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buying his silence, huh? {\alpha&HFF&}It's best to assume that he already knows something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.18,0:18:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buying his silence, huh? It's best to assume that he already knows something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting too dangerous! {\alpha&HFF&}I want out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.12,0:18:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting too dangerous! I want out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got no clue to which one of you is Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}but I don't want to get too deep in this and end up being arrested!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.04,0:18:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got no clue to which one of you is Kira, but I don't want to get too deep in this and end up being arrested!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.93,0:18:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hatori... {\alpha&HFF&}you're going to be dead tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hatori... you're going to be dead tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that was just a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.97,0:18:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in! I'll do this properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what're we gonna do? {\alpha&HFF&}Even if Coil knows something, he's still willing to take it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what're we gonna do? Even if Coil knows something, he's still willing to take it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.84,0:18:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we give him the money, he's on our side. {\alpha&HFF&}That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.27,0:18:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we give him the money, he's on our side. That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:18:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to keep a shrewd guy like him on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right; it doesn't matter how much we've got to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right! Buy him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, this contract with Coil, {\alpha&HFF&}any objections?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, this contract with Coil, any objections?
